* {{книга|заглавие=The goal: Bobby Orr and the most famous goal in Stanley Cup history|автор= Andrew Podnieks|год=2003|Triumph Books. |ref=Podnieks}}
* {{книга|заглавие=The Power of Two: The Carl Brewer Story. Bolton|автор= Susan Foster|год=2006|ON: Fenn Publishing. |isbn = 978-1-55168-289-1.|ref=Dryden}}

